      ('493c3659-1852-4243-8d7b-ab11132fb836', 'ce7debe9-796b-48df-a17c-f5e1c91cd012', 'description', 'ISO/IEC 27001:2022 is an international standard for establishing, implementing, maintaining, and continually improving an Information Security Management System (ISMS). It provides a risk-based approach for protecting information assets through organizational, people, physical, and technological controls. The framework supports systematic identification of security risks, implementation of appropriate safeguards, continuous monitoring, and improvement of security practices to ensure confidentiality, integrity, and availability of information.', '2026-03-26T05:11:09.3409', '2026-03-26T05:11:09.3409', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
